1. It is for method reuse and we can pass it like lambda functions. Shorthand for Lambda
2. More readable
3. For example, Apple::getWeight is a method reference to the method getWeight defined in the Apple class.
   Remember that no brackets are needed because you’re not actually calling the method.
4. (Apple a)->a.getWeight()  ===> short hand Apple :: getWeight

=====================
Constructor references :::
======================

->